race.description: Evergreen Turf Nrra Championships Qualifier Plate (C5)
race.comment: Matt Dunn holds the aces, and the top three selections all represent his barn. CONSIDERED (9) seeks the hat-trick off a Highway win at Rosehill. Has been kept on the fresh side, and the inside barrier should advantage. Winning rider Mallyon goes back on. KINGDOM UNDERSIEGE (3) has similar numbers. He delivered the hat-trick in a Randwick Highway three weeks ago following a big 66 win at Lismore. Has the outside barrier in a 14-horse field, but Nash Rawiller is up from Sydney to stick aboard. MOSCOW CIRCUS (12) was quickly back to form winning a 74 at Port Macquarie as expected. Tumbles in weight today and that brings her into it. SAMMY CONQUERS ALL (1) resumes and is good enough to feature if presented forward. Won a recent Grafton trial so keep a close eye on the betting.
